      Everything You Need to Stay Connected
    </h2>
    <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 30px;">
      
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div style="
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        width: 300px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
